com.desafio.ponto.model

Interface PontoMarcacoesModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.liferay.portal.kernel.model.BaseModel<PontoMarcacoes>, com.liferay.portal.kernel.model.ClassedModel, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable<PontoMarcacoes>, java.io.Serializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    PontoMarcacoes
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PontoMarcacoesBaseImpl, PontoMarcacoesImpl, PontoMarcacoesModelImpl, PontoMarcacoesWrapper

    @ProviderType
public interface PontoMarcacoesModel
extends com.liferay.portal.kernel.model.BaseModel<PontoMarcacoes>
    The base model interface for the PontoMarcacoes service. Represents a row in the "ponto_marcacao" database table, with each column mapped to a property of this class.

    This interface and its corresponding implementation PontoMarcacoesModelImpl exist only as a container for the default property accessors generated by ServiceBuilder. Helper methods and all application logic should be put in PontoMarcacoesImpl.

    Author:
    Peterson Morais
    See Also:
    PontoMarcacoes, PontoMarcacoesImpl, PontoMarcacoesModelImpl
